<TEXT>
a cattle rancher and his son were 
convicted of firstdegree murder saturday for killing chico mendes 
the rain forest defender whose death focused global attention on 
the destruction of the amazon 
the defendants were each sentenced to 19 years in prison at the 
end of the fourday trial the prosecutors accusing the ranchers 
of having stained the forest with his blood had urged the 
maximum 30year sentence 
the sevenmember jury decided darly alves da silva planned the 
dec 22 1988 slaying and that his son darci alves pereira fired 
the shotgun that killed mendes 
scores of mendes supporters and relatives who jammed the tiny 
sweltering wooden courthouse burst into applause when judge adair 
longhini read the verdict after conferring with the jury for more 
than three hours 
ilzamar mendes the slain rubber tappers widow burst into 
tears 
osmarino amancio rodrigues seen as mendes successor in the 
rubber tappers union that campaigns against destruction of the 
forest joined hands with other tappers and flashed a v sign 
defense attorney ruben torres said his clients would appeal 
you cant judge a man guilty on false testimony said dari 
da silva alves da silvas brother 
the trial in this amazon river town 2650 miles northwest of rio 
de janeiro opened wednesday with the surprise murder confession by 
23yearold alves pereira who claimed he had acted alone his 
father fought the charges 
the trial caused a sensation in this nation of 150 million 
where mendes 44 is seen as an ecological martyr who died 
defending the vast amazon jungle from slashandburn destruction by 
ranchers and farmers 
the amazon is the worlds largest rain forest and the only 
habitat for many plant and animal species rubber tappers and 
others depend on the forest for their livelihood but once the 
jungle is cleared it becomes barren of most vegetation within a few 
years 
a texassized chunk of the forest already has been cut down 
prosecutor marcio thomaz bastos a former brazilian bar 
association president said it was the first time in brazil that 
the planner of a slaying had been convicted of murder 
darci and darly surely practiced many other crimes said the 
jubilant bastos this trial should serve as a lever so we can 
open up other cases 
the 54yearold alves da silva slumped in his chair and pressed 
a white handkerchief to his face during closing arguments as bastos 
shouted you killed him you 
bastos had said a verdict of guilty would end an atmosphere of 
terror in the far western amazon state of acre where rich 
landowners often use hired gunmen to eliminate their opponents 
in his threehour closing statement defense attorney ruben 
lopes torres said alves pereira was so perturbed by the mounting 
legal pressure mendes was applying against his father that he was 
pushed into committing the murder 
mendes in 1988 led local rubber tappers and their families to 
stand in front of bulldozers ready to clear virgin forest owned by 
alves da silva 
earlier saturday about 150 people attended a dawn vigil at the 
tomb of mendes who would have been 46 on saturday 
the group of relatives rubber tappers and foreign visitors then 
walked to mendes humble wooden house near the town square for a 
memorial ceremony in memory of his birthday 
it was two years ago that chico told me he would be spending 
his last birthday with me said a weeping ilzamar mendes he 
still lives within the people that are carrying on his work 
on a small wooden table in front of the house now coverted into 
a museum and headquarters of the chico mendes foundation lay the 
united nations global 500 award mendes earned in 1987 for his 
defense of the environment 
an elderly rubber tapper stepped forward and silently placed a 
small metal rubber tapping knife on the table 
rodrigues who is under police protection because of death 
threats unfolded a map of the chico mendes extractivist reserve 
created by the government last year the reserve allows rubber 
tappers to commercially harvest latex nuts and other forest 
products a dream of mendes 
a 2by2 foot block of fresh concrete was laid on the muddy 
ground beside the back door of the house where mendes was hit by 
the shotgun blast 
with a wooden stick a rubber tapper traced the words here 
they killed chico mendes the fight continues 
</TEXT>
